msgid "# New-DfsReplicationGroup"
msgstr "# 新DFS复制组"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "Creates a replication group."
msgstr "创建一个复制组。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 描述"

msgid ""
"The **New-DfsReplicationGroup** cmdlet creates a replication group.\n"
"A replication group is a set of servers, or members, that participate in the replication of one or more folders.\n"
"A replicated folder is kept synchronized among the members of a replication group.\n"
"This cmdlet cannot modify resource group bandwidth or schedules."
msgstr ""
"`New-DfsReplicationGroup` cmdlet "
"用于创建一个复制组。复制组是由一组服务器组成的集合，这些服务器参与一个或多个文件夹的复制过程。被复制的文件夹会在复制组的成员之间保持同步状态。此 "
"cmdlet 无法修改资源组的带宽或调度设置。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Create a replication group"
msgstr "### 示例 1：创建一个复制组"

msgid "This command creates a replication group named RG01."
msgstr "该命令创建了一个名为RG01的复制组。"

msgid "### Example 2: Create a replication topology"
msgstr "#### 示例 2：创建复制拓扑结构"

msgid ""
"This example creates a replication topology with an upstream server and two "
"downstream servers."
msgstr "这个示例创建了一个复制拓扑结构，其中包含一个上游服务器和两个下游服务器。"

msgid ""
"The first command uses the **New-DfsReplicationGroup** cmdlet to create a replication group with the name Branch Office 1.\n"
"The command pipes the output to the **New-DfsReplicatedFolder** cmdlet to create a replicated folder with the name Data Distribution 1.\n"
"The command pipes the output to the **Add-DfsrMember** cmdlet to add the member servers named SRV01, SRV02, and SRV03.\n"
"The command formats the output of the pipeline as a table."
msgstr ""
"第一个命令使用 **New-DfsReplicationGroup** cmdlet 创建一个名为 “Branch Office 1” "
"的复制组。该命令将输出结果传递给 **New-DfsReplicatedFolder** cmdlet，以创建一个名为 “Data "
"Distribution 1” 的复制备份文件夹。接着，该命令将输出结果再次传递给 **Add-DfsrMember** "
"cmdlet，用于添加成员服务器 SRV01、SRV02 和 SRV03。最后，该命令将整个处理流程的输出结果格式化为表格形式。"

msgid ""
"The second command uses the **Add-DfsrConnection** cmdlet to add "
"bidirectional connections between servers SRV01 and SRV02."
msgstr "第二个命令使用了 **Add-DfsrConnection** cmdlet，在服务器 SRV01 和 SRV02 之间建立双向连接。"

msgid ""
"The third command uses the **Add-DfsrConnection** cmdlet to add "
"bidirectional connections between servers SRV01 and SRV03."
msgstr "第三个命令使用了 **Add-DfsrConnection** cmdlet 来在 SRV01 和 SRV03 服务器之间建立双向连接。"

msgid ""
"The fourth command uses the **Set-DfsrMembership** cmdlet to set SRV01 as "
"the primary member."
msgstr "第四条命令使用 **Set-DfsrMembership** cmdlet 将 SRV01 设置为主要成员。"

msgid ""
"The fifth command uses the **Set-DfsrMembership** cmdlet to set membership "
"for servers SRV02 and SRV03."
msgstr "第五条命令使用了 **Set-DfsrMembership** cmdlet 来设置 SRV02 和 SRV03 服务器的成员身份。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid "Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet."
msgstr "在运行 cmdlet 之前会提示您进行确认。"

msgid "Specifies a description for the replication group."
msgstr "为复制组指定一个描述。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the NetBIOS name or fully qualified domain name (FQDN) for the Active Directory Domain Service (AD DS) domain that contains a replication group.\n"
"If you do not specify this parameter, the cmdlet uses the current domain."
msgstr ""
"指定包含复制组的 Active Directory 域服务（AD DS）域的 NetBIOS "
"名称或完全限定域名（FQDN）。如果不指定此参数，cmdlet 将使用当前域。"

msgid "Specifies an array of names of replication groups."
msgstr "指定一个复制组名称的数组。"

msgid ""
"Shows what would happen if the cmdlet runs.\n"
"The cmdlet is not run."
msgstr "展示了如果运行该cmdlet会发生什么情况。但实际上并没有运行该cmdlet。"

